The Topic Modelling Tool I've found most useful was created by S. Enderle. I've used this on my own work with great success! Click here for a tutorial and downloading instructions:
https://senderle.github.io/topic-modeling-tool/documentation/2017/01/06/quickstart.html

Alternately, you can take a text file and run it through Voyant Tools, which will give you more visualization options:
https://voyant-tools.org
